	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Try not to lick your circuitry in general.
<br />
<br />The materials used to change the conductive properties of the silicon in IC's are poisonous, arsenic is one of them. Also non ROHS compliant ones will contain lead.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


