	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Definitely don't do anything like that. Even putting the chips in liquid and then drinking just the liquid is a bad idea. While it won't necessarily make you drop dead right away they are unlikely to be harmless. Particularly if you haven't cleaned the objects first. Given there age and where they have been who knows what trace amounts of bad things are on them. And alcohol might actually be worse than water alone to be drinking after putting old dirty ICs in it.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


